---
title: Quick Double Seared Rump Steak & Garlic Butter with Roast Root Veggie Toss & Creamy Pesto Dressing
description: We’ve dug deep to create this stunning meal for tonight’s dinner. A roast root veggie toss, with pops of colour from the beetroot, adds an earthy flavour to the succulent beef rump, slathered in a buttery garlic sauce. We know you will be excavating this plate down to the last crumb.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
